Accuracy

The ratio of correctly predicted instances to total instances. Works best when classes are balanced.

Precision & Recall
Precision: How many predicted positives are actually correct
Recall: How many actual positives were correctly identified
Useful in cases like fraud detection or medical diagnosis.
Train/Test Split

The dataset is divided into training and testing sets. The model learns from the training set and is evaluated on the test set to check its performance on unseen data.
